Package: dgeContrasts
Type: Package
Title: Create contrasts for use with Differential Gene Expression Analysis packages such as edgeR, limma-voom and DESeq2
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Huzefa Khalil
Maintainer: Huzefa Khalil <huzefa.khalil@umich.edu>
Description: The package provides a function to create contrasts for use with Differential Gene Expression Analysis packages such as edgeR, limma-voom and DESeq2. Two-way interactions are supported, but only for factors with two levels. The script can handle unbalanced designs as well. Contrasts can be created for all possible comparisons.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
